title: Eaton BR230B Plug-On Mount Circuit Breaker 2-Pole 30 Amp 120/240 Volt AC
description: Eaton Type BR circuit breaker is a 2-Pole, 1-Phase breaker with interrupt rating of 10 Kilo-Amps. This circuit breaker is current rated at 30 Amps and voltage rated at 120/240 Volts AC. The plug-on breaker features thermal magnetic tripping and rejection tab. It accommodates copper/aluminum wire of size 14 to 4 AWG. Circuit breaker meets UL 489 and Federal Specifications Classification W-C375 standards.
